= Simple Usage

== One-Line Installation & Running

*Installation & Run:* Just use pipx - no complex setup required!

#pause

```bash
# Install and run directly
pipx run all-in-mcp

# With specific tool modules enabled
APAPER=true GITHUB_REPO_MCP=true pipx run all-in-mcp
```


